<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('./partials/head.ejs', {
        pageTitle: 'About | Harmony Wellness Group, Tampa FL',
        pageDescription: 'Learn about Harmony Wellness Group in Tampa—our philosophy, team approach, and commitment to your recovery.'
  }) %>
<body class="antialiased">
  <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs', { navVariant: 'solid' }) %>

<main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-50 via-white to-green-100 pt-12">    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <img
            src="/about.JPG"
            alt="Harmony Wellness Group care team in Tampa, Florida"
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <a href="/services" class="px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-emerald-700 text-white hover:bg-emerald-600 transition">
              View Services
            </a>
            <a href="/request-appointment" class="px-5 py-3 rounded-xl border border-emerald-700 text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50 transition">
              Request an Appointment
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">About Harmony Wellness Group</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-7 mb-4">
            Harmony Wellness Group is a modern rehabilitation and wellness clinic dedicated to helping you move, heal, and feel your best. We combine evidence-based care with a calm, supportive environment—so recovery feels reassuring from the moment you walk in.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-7 mb-4">
            Our team collaborates across disciplines to personalize your plan, whether you’re healing from an injury, managing chronic pain, or aiming to improve mobility and performance. We focus on practical progress, clear communication, and sustainable results.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-7 mb-6">
            From your first assessment to your final session, we meet you where you are and guide you forward—one step at a time.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3 text-gray-900">Our Care Philosophy</h2>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-gray-800">
            <li class="bg-white/90 rounded-xl shadow p-4"><strong>Patient-First</strong> — Your goals drive the plan.</li>
            <li class="bg-white/90 rounded-xl shadow p-4"><strong>Evidence-Based</strong> — Methods rooted in the latest research.</li>
            <li class="bg-white/90 rounded-xl shadow p-4"><strong>Collaborative</strong> — Clinicians who listen and adapt.</li>
            <li class="bg-white/90 rounded-xl shadow p-4"><strong>Sustainable</strong> — Progress you can maintain beyond the clinic.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>